WEBVTT

00:01.921 --> 00:03.825
<i>Your disease.</i>
What are you doing about it?

00:03.828 --> 00:06.038
Regular examinations,
calibrated meds.

00:06.072 --> 00:07.546
You appear free from
physical symptoms,

00:07.580 --> 00:10.088
but I'm far more concerned
about mental decline,

00:10.122 --> 00:12.465
- <i>hallucinations.</i>
- Boss.

00:12.499 --> 00:15.107
- His name is Chad Langley.
- You're sure he's the one?

00:15.141 --> 00:17.180
The high-powered rifle
in the trunk of his car

00:17.215 --> 00:18.987
matches the bullet
that struck your wife.

00:19.022 --> 00:22.534
- When can I see you?
- You shouldn't-- not worth the risk.

00:22.568 --> 00:24.940
- You don't want to hear this.
- Kitty O'Neill's joined the Walsh camp.

00:24.975 --> 00:27.215
- Campaign managing?
- Cut the bullshit, Kitty.

00:27.249 --> 00:29.524
- Town hall at UIC.
- Pass.

00:29.558 --> 00:32.601
<i>I know, by the way,
about you and Ben.</i>

00:32.636 --> 00:35.342
- Town hall, Evanston.
- Fine.

00:38.286 --> 00:39.958
Oh, I love you.

00:39.992 --> 00:41.398
Is that your wife
in the picture?

00:41.432 --> 00:43.369
Nah, a couple of good-time
girls, that's all.

00:43.405 --> 00:45.977
<i>We used to have to beat them
off with a stick back then.</i>

00:46.011 --> 00:48.719
I have information that every
media outlet in town wants--

00:48.753 --> 00:51.159
the name of the suspect in the
shooting of Meredith Kane.

00:51.193 --> 00:52.195
Do we have a deal?

00:52.229 --> 00:54.670
Sir, posted online too.

00:54.704 --> 00:56.340
God damn it.

00:56.375 --> 00:58.246
Gentlemen, I wanted to present
this redevelopment plan

00:58.280 --> 01:00.318
in person because of
its tremendous scope.

01:00.352 --> 01:03.428
With all due respect, it's just not
practical to move that quickly.

01:03.462 --> 01:06.334
Natural selection.
We adapt or we die.

01:06.368 --> 01:08.475
Hired some
out-of-state contractor

01:08.509 --> 01:10.581
who's supposed to do it
all on the cheap.

01:10.615 --> 01:12.719
No one man is bigger
than the machine.

01:12.754 --> 01:13.956
It corrects itself.

01:13.990 --> 01:15.895
I haven't set foot here
for over 20 years.

01:15.929 --> 01:17.298
I haven't
protected you.

01:17.332 --> 01:19.906
Don't listen to this shit.
Kane is a goddamn liar.

01:19.940 --> 01:24.250
And when you do come home, the likes
of Kenya Taylor will not be here.

01:24.284 --> 01:27.258
Fuck you, Kane.
You can't change shit!

01:27.292 --> 01:30.634
I'm not done yet.
The thugs-- criminal and financial,

01:30.669 --> 01:32.873
have no idea
what's coming.

